              "path": "/people/narrators/41",
              "text": "عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ سِنَانٍ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " عَنْ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "narrator",
              "path": "/people/narrators/19",
              "text": "أَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام )"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " قَالَ"
            }
          ],
          "text": "ابْنُ مَحْبُوبٍ عَنْ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ سِنَانٍ عَنْ أَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) قَالَ"
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/al-kafi:2:4:27:2",
        "text": [
          " رَدُّ جَوَابِ الْكِتَابِ وَاجِبٌ كَوُجُوبِ رَدِّ السَّلَامِ وَ الْبَادِي بِالسَّلَامِ أَوْلَى بِاللَّهِ وَ رَسُولِهِ ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.hubeali": [
            "Ibn Mahboub, from Abdullah Bin Sinan, ",
            "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Returning an answer to a letter is as Obligatory as the Obligation of returning the greeting, and the initiator of the greeting is closer with Allah<sup>azwj</sup> and His<sup>azwj</sup> Rasool<sup>saww</sup>’."
          ],
          "en.sarwar": [
            "2. Ibn Mahbub has narrated from ‘Abd Allah ibn Sinan from abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who has said the following: “It is necessary to reply a letter just as it is necessary to answer a greeting of peace. The initiator of a greeting of peace is closer to Allah and His messenger.” "
          ]
        }
      }
